title: La Cocinita Verde. Comidas Rapidas
typeOfFood: Vegan, Western, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Bakery, Colombian
description: Fast food eatery, est. Dec 2015 ( formerly Pan de Nobles Express). Offers burgers made from gluten, soy, lentils, falafel and quinoa, tofu. Has hot dogs, paella, and lasagna. Delivers weekdays 12-4pm to 10 block radius .
